{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"39753-rabbit-becomes-a-chef","title":"Rabbit Becomes a Chef","description":"Raw carrots for breakfast. Raw carrots for lunch. Raw carrots for dinner. Rabbit is tired of eating raw carrots and wants to learn how to cook them into a tasty curry. ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Magdalena  Cooper"],"illustrators":["Chamath Prasanga Lokuliyana"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/39753-rabbit-becomes-a-chef"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/105036/size3/18f8fd4a121fc54acd71d658d4013da8.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/105036/size6/18f8fd4a121fc54acd71d658d4013da8.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75109/size6/d7852db038112530226f80bc511d6173.jpg","text":"“Every day, I eat only raw carrots,” Rabbit said to herself.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75110/size6/7ea92a1351cf79e5a3c607555aeb0002.jpg","text":"\"I'm tired of raw carrots!\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75111/size6/6c09b4a0879bc768a7723dc40e6d40cf.jpg","text":"“What can I do to make these better?\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75112/size6/5652eae4fc57ede6ea42fa8fc3a31c38.jpg","text":"That afternoon, she went to farmer's house and saw a pot boiling over the fire.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75113/size6/34fa4ee3def2cc4b6322fc52b4526e6c.jpg","text":"Just as she started to have an idea the farmer’s dog came barking after her.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75114/size6/49585906913abf40f362287807eefc2f.jpg","text":"“Hmm,\" thought rabbit. \"What should I do now?\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75115/size6/820e709f5a62b70ba4c603720f0e4a3b.jpg","text":"Rabbit tried leaving the carrots in the sun. \nBut, the carrots remained just as raw as before.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75117/size6/44889d693ef5ce0d50db022021815cb5.jpg","text":"Then, she tried putting them in the fire. \nWhen she tasted them, they were bitter!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75118/size6/dacab5fa1b93ac1b681279114584ceff.jpg","text":"She thought and thought and thought \nabout what to do.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75119/size6/ffddd85db5a2c059e4aa403e8cde851b.jpg","text":"Finally, she had an idea! \nFirst, she found an old tortoise shell.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75120/size6/66d6676568df57ad27fc11ac0d3e90b0.jpg","text":"Then, she collected some sticks","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75121/size6/83af7793713cbc3f8fc68fa8e680b1a4.jpg","text":"And three stones.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75122/size6/e35ad5dbab7820fd4785965ab2ce424a.jpg","text":"Hooray! Rabbit finally had a way too cook her carrots.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75123/size6/26e3080ff22efd06438d18b714fb1e44.jpg","text":"She was so excited that she invited all her friends.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75124/size6/5993fdf5cf5895db8ecdca89cd5d583f.jpg","text":"And they all had a meal of delicious cooked carrots.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":154}}